the aim of this project is to help me grow closer to Allah swt, our creator.
to love Allah is to know Allah, and to know Allah is to know his names.
i dont know his names by heart so that quote spoke volumes to me
i sat thinking i wish there was an app that could send reminders each day or week of one attribute of allah, to help reflect throughout the day
most apps would have premium versions or something complicated
my initiative was to build something for myself and inshaa allaah for others to use as well

started with the help of claude ai to draw a spec of instructions on how to build this application

techstack used:

- react frontend
- node.js backend
- supabase database
- resend emails
- render to deploy backend

the core mechanism is the node-cron scheduler that runs on my server at a set time each day
it looks up the next name in the sequence and fires off an email with the arabix, transliteration, meaning and soon the reflection
